WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.179 --> 00:00:03.319
This is the admin side of Lesson Spot.

2
00:00:03.319 --> 00:00:04.500
When a parent books,

3
00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:06.639
it lands right on your dashboard.

4
00:00:06.639 --> 00:00:08.739
Every lesson, every player,

5
00:00:08.739 --> 00:00:11.739
every note, all in one place.

6
00:00:11.739 --> 00:00:15.099
Coaching notes stay private between you and the athlete.

7
00:00:15.099 --> 00:00:17.699
Upload swing video, drills,

8
00:00:17.699 --> 00:00:20.000
anything you want them to review before the next

9
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.559
session. The Resources tab lets athletes access your full

10
00:00:24.559 --> 00:00:27.219
library of videos and forms.

11
00:00:27.219 --> 00:00:28.659
You set your own hours,

12
00:00:28.659 --> 00:00:30.119
your own lesson types,

13
00:00:30.119 --> 00:00:32.659
your own pricing, and you can split a day

14
00:00:32.659 --> 00:00:36.180
into multiple windows, like a morning solo block and

15
00:00:36.180 --> 00:00:38.099
an afternoon group block,

16
00:00:38.099 --> 00:00:40.360
each with its own mode.

17
00:00:40.360 --> 00:00:41.979
Running with other coaches?

18
00:00:41.979 --> 00:00:44.040
Each one gets their own calendar,

19
00:00:44.040 --> 00:00:46.079
lesson types, and bookings,

20
00:00:46.079 --> 00:00:48.059
all under your brand.

21
00:00:48.059 --> 00:00:50.479
Email reminders go out automatically,

22
00:00:50.479 --> 00:00:53.319
so you stop chasing kids the night before.

23
00:00:53.319 --> 00:00:55.219
Your page is fully branded.

24
00:00:55.219 --> 00:00:57.599
Your logo, your hero photo,

25
00:00:57.599 --> 00:01:00.039
your colors, your name.

26
00:01:00.039 --> 00:01:02.819
This is how you stop juggling DMs and group

27
00:01:02.819 --> 00:01:05.519
chats and run lessons like a real business
